        <h1>
            Register for Final Project Grading
        </h1>
        <p style="text-align: justify">
            Please register below for final project grading.
            Provide the URL of your project hosted on OpenShift,
            and the URL of the GitHub repository where you
            have the source code of your project.
            Make sure the project is always at a stable usable
            state.
            You will be texted/emailed shortly before we start
            grading
            your project. Please stop all development when you
            receive the text/email.
            The final grading order will be settled on midnight
            Sunday EST,
            before grading actually starts.
            Anyone not registered by midnight Sunday EST will be
            graded before the ones that register in no particular
            order.
        </p>
